1.Manage jenkins > terraform ( 1.0.10 )

2.Global tool configuration:
Name: terraform
remove install automatically
Install directory:/usr/local/bin/terraform 
apply>save


-------------------------------------------


Freestyle job > Name: workspace>create
Configure:
choice para >> Name:env , value:prod dev
Restrict label : jenkinsmaster
git : https://github.com/saravananajay/own-terraform-code.git, branch : main
Build env>>delete workspace before build starts
Build steps >> execute shell

cd $WORKSPACE/terraform-code/workspaces
terraform init
terraform workspace new $env
terraform workspace select $env
terraform apply -var-file="$env.tfvars" --auto-approve
apply>save


Build with parameters
env: choose env
Build
